  m_Name: 1.a
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Lines:
  - ...I am sure your mom will be very happy to hear that.
  - Because as I was being brought into this world, I could clearly feel how much
    she loved you.
  - 'During those years when she could not be with you, she always felt deeply guilty. '
  - She has always loved and missed you, without ever stopping.
  ReplyOptions:
  - line: Ask about leaving.
    nextNode: {fileID: 11400000, guid: fa7a8359162dc7449ab205b06f0990f7, type: 2}
    favorChange: -1
    requiredFavor: 0
    endDialogue: 0
    playerLine: If she loved me, why did she leave?
  - line: Share your feeling.
